091EA8DD.Line13.6D03F: Everything happened exactly as Lilith wanted. We just danced to her music.

3D079BE1.Line17.6D03F: No one knew what Lilith was truly after, or exactly what Astaroth had promised her.

5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: Lilith and Astaroth had made a deal, and we were the ones who would pay the cost.

A313225F.Line15.6D03F: Donan was shattered, his mind on grief, not her. Not answers.

D6FC1563.Line19.6D03F: But we needed to recover quickly...and we needed to stop chasing her phantoms.
